item.title: crossbow semiprestige 2023
item.description: Tech Guide Location: Rutland Park, Calgary Course: stravalink I missed out on writing this up at the end of the 2023 CX season, and now that 2024 has come around, I don’t have a bunch of the data I like to put in these race writeups. Nonetheless, here’s what I can find (thankfully I did do my CrossResults upload back when the race happened). This race was postponed from earlier in the month because of some freakish weather.
